{"tid":1316971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有咁嘅實力，721絕對要對準雙普選！","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:52:11.000Z","uid":90486,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85f92abeceeeaf97adb82d41d1d80020060f255c","tid":1316971,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"今日證明咗我地有實力，亦有支持。<br />\n<br />\n好多和理非覺得林奠壽終正寢已經回應咗訴求，開始出現疲態；同埋雖然支持者睇住啲狗俾人打睇得好開心，但漸漸<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持者已經唔記得我地訴求係乜</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n今次運動嘅民氣係多年成果，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果林奠突然撒回+下台，到時市民一覺得政府讓咗步，民氣一散唔知儲幾耐先儲得返</span></span>，今次運動聲勢浩大到係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只此一次，有今生冇來世</span>[/red]<br />\n<br />\n而且要解決困局，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔能夠只係政府一時三刻喺個別問題跪低，而係要改革整個政制！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗5大訴求外，我地有咁嘅實力同民氣，已經有能力同政府叫價，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721應該將矛頭指向雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721，釋放義士、獨立調查委員會、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雙普選！</span>。"},{"pid":"64f80caba061a9b29f3669b5a65dbf1c4408cc82","tid":1316971,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e41a6b1072f2058b75d788db5662b20c35e8dc","tid":1316971,"uid":77416,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJXWj2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJXWj2F.jpg&h=7a01a3c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"836f80f6a5aea09ae588433342f3b3b4095584c3","tid":1316971,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68b0ad19924e7ba5ea66de84e674869e817076e3","tid":1316971,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"真普選"},{"pid":"d98d6d60c23c9c57d18ba20a447f3123